         <xs:element minOccurs="0" name="Section_F">
            
            
            <xs:annotation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="FieldText">
                  Altered Space Conditioning System Duct Information (
                  <ns1:lt/>
                   75% of duct system is altered; or duct system is not altered)
               </xs:documentation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If section is required If at least one SC system in section B has B04 == true And  B10_ResidentialHvacAlterationType  == DuctSystemExistingExtended  Or SpaceConditioningSystemAltered For each SC System in section B  which satisfy these conditions do the following:  A. Require one row of data for each SC system in section D D02 for which  C03_ResidentialHeatingSystemType  == GasPackagedFurnace.  B. Require one row of data for each SC system in section E E02 where C07_ResidentialCoolingSystemType  == CentralPackagedAC, CentralPackagedHP CentralLargePackagedAC, Or  CentralLargePackagedHP  And same packkaged unit is not already listed in section D thus D02 !- E02.     C. If C13_DuctedIndoorUnitsCount GTE 1 require one row of data to be entered in this table for each of that quantity.</xs:documentation>
               
               
               <xs:documentation source="MinOccurs">If this section doesn't apply, display only the section FieldText and the statement 'This section does not apply to this project.'</xs:documentation>
               
            
            </xs:annotation>
            
            
            <xs:complexType>
               
               
               <xs:sequence>
                  
                  
                  <xs:element name="TableAlteredSCDucts">
                     
                     
                     <xs:annotation>
                        
                        
                        <xs:documentation source="FieldText"/>
                        
                     
                     </xs:annotation>
                     
                     
                     <xs:complexType>
                        
                        
                        <xs:sequence>
                           
                           
                           <xs:element maxOccurs="unbounded" minOccurs="1" name="Row">
                              
                              
                              <xs:complexType>
                                 
                                 
                                 <xs:sequence>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:element name="F01_ResidentialSpaceConditioningSystemName" type="hvac:ResidentialSpaceConditioningSystemName">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="FieldText">SC System ID/ Name from parent CC</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">Reference value from B01_ResidentialSpaceConditioningSystemName</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:annotation>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:element>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:element name="F02_ResidentialHvacSystemAreaServed" type="hvac:ResidentialHvacSystemAreaServed">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="FieldText">SC System Description of Area Served</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">Reference value from B02_ResidentialHvacSystemAreaServed</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:annotation>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:element>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:element name="F03_IndoorUnitName" type="hvac:IndoorUnitName">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Indoor Unit Name or  Description of  Area Served</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If any of these conditions are true: C03_ResidentialHeatingSystemType == GasPackagedFurnace; C03_ResidentialHeatingSystemType Or C07_ResidentialCoolingSystemType  == CentralPackagedAC, CentralPackagedHP CentralLargePackagedAC, Or  CentralLargePackagedHP;  Or C12_IndoorUnitsCount = 1 then result = B02_ResidentialHvacSystemAreaServed;  Else If C12_IndoorUnitsCount GT 1 And D10_IndoorUnitDucts  IsPresent And D10_IndoorUnitDucts == DuctsLTE10Ft Or  DuctsGT10Ft result = D09_IndoorUnitName; Else user input maximum 15 characters;  Do not allow duplicate values for indoor unit names in this Mch01 as listed in F03 and G03</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:annotation>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:element>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:element name="F04_NewDuctingInstalled" type="comp:NewDuctingInstalled">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Was Any New Ducting Installed?</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">User selects from list;  SupplyAndReturn display term Both Supply and Return, NoNewDucts display term No, SupplyOnly display term Supply Only, RetrunOnly display term Return Only</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:annotation>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:element>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:choice maxOccurs="1">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F05_DuctRValueLimit">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Required New Duct R-Value</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled == NoNewDucts  
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage; 
Else If B07_Installing40PlusLinearFeetDucts == false 
result = R6; 
Else If A02_ClimateZone == 3, 5, 6 or 7
result = R6;
 Else If  A02_ClimateZone == 1, 2, 4 or InRange (8, 16) 
result = R8.
End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:simpleType>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:restriction base="hvac:DuctRValueLimit">
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R6"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R8"/>
                                                
                                             
                                             </xs:restriction>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:simpleType>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F05_NotApplicableMessage" type="comp:NotApplicableMessage">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Required New Duct R-Value</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled == NoNewDucts  
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage; 
End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:choice>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:choice maxOccurs="1">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F06_SupplyDuctLocation">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed New Supply Duct Location</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  NoNewDucts Or ReturnOnly result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage; 
                                                Else If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  SupplyAndReturn Or SupplyOnly 
                                                user selects from list: 
                                                ConditionedSpace display term Conditioned space-entirely 
                                                UnconditionedAttic display term Unconditioned attic 
                                                UnconditionedCrawlSpace display term Unconditioned crawl space
                                                ControlledVentilationCrawlSpace display term Controlled ventilation crawl space
                                                UnconditionedGarage display term Unconditioned garage 
                                                UnconditionedBasement display term Unconditioned basement 
                                                Outdoors display term Outdoors End if</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:simpleType>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:restriction base="hvac:SupplyDuctLocation">
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="ConditionedSpace"/>
                                                                                            
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="ControlledVentilationCrawlSpace"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="Outdoors"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="UnconditionedAttic"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="UnconditionedBasement"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="UnconditionedCrawlSpace"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="UnconditionedGarage"/>
                                                
                                             
                                             </xs:restriction>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:simpleType>
                                           
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F06_NotApplicableMessage" type="comp:NotApplicableMessage">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed New Supply Duct Location</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  NoNewDucts Or ReturnOnly 
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage; 
End if</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:choice>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:choice maxOccurs="1">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F07_DuctRValue">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed New Supply Duct R-value</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  NoNewDucts Or ReturnOnly 
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage; 
 
Else If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  SupplyAndReturn Or SupplyOnly 
user selects from list: 
R-0.0, R-2.1, R4.2, R-6,  R-8, R-10 and R-12.  
End If
 
Check value for compliance:  
If result == R-0.0, R-2.1, R4.2 And F10_DuctMinimumRValueExceptions == RValueLT6EntirelyInConditioned 
result complies; 
Else If result  GTE F05_DuctRvaluelimit 
result complies; 
Else 
Flag result as non-compliance and do not allow registration to proceed if not in compliance;
End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:simpleType>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:restriction base="hvac:DuctRValue">
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R0.0"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R10"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R12"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R2.1"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R4.2"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R6"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R8"/>
                                                
                                             
                                             </xs:restriction>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:simpleType>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F07_NotApplicableMessage" type="comp:NotApplicableMessage">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed New Supply Duct R-value</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  NoNewDucts Or ReturnOnly 
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage; 
End if</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:choice>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:choice maxOccurs="1">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F08_ReturnDuctLocation">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed New Return Duct Location</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  NoNewDucts Or SupplyOnly result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage; 
                                             Else If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  SupplyAndReturn Or ReturnOnly 
                                             user selects from list: 
                                              ConditionedSpace display term Conditioned space-entirely
                                             UnconditionedAttic display term Unconditioned attic
                                             UnconditionedCrawlSpace display term Unconditioned crawl space
                                             ControlledVentilationCrawlSpace display term Controlled ventilation crawl space
                                             UnconditionedGarage display term Unconditioned garage
                                             UnconditionedBasement display term Unconditioned basement
                                             Outdoors display term Outdoors
                                             End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:simpleType>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:restriction base="hvac:ReturnDuctLocation">
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="ConditionedSpace"/>
                                                                                            
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="ControlledVentilationCrawlSpace"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="Outdoors"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="UnconditionedAttic"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="UnconditionedBasement"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="UnconditionedCrawlSpace"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="UnconditionedGarage"/>
                                                
                                             
                                             </xs:restriction>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:simpleType>
                                           
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F08_NotApplicableMessage" type="comp:NotApplicableMessage">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed New Return Duct Location</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  NoNewDucts Or SupplyOnly 
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage; 
End if</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:choice>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:choice maxOccurs="1">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F09_DuctRValue">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed New Return Duct R-Value</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  NoNewDucts Or SupplyOnly 
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage; 
 
Else If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  SupplyAndReturn Or ReturnOnly 
user selects from list: 
R-0.0, R-2.1, R4.2, R-6,  R-8, R-10 and R-12.  
End If
 
Check value for compliance:  
If result == R-0.0, R-2.1, R4.2 And F10_DuctMinimumRValueExceptions == RValueLT6EntirelyInConditioned 
result complies; 
Else If result  GTE F05_DuctRvaluelimit 
result complies; 
Else 
Flag result as non-compliance and do not allow registration to proceed if not in compliance;
End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:simpleType>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:restriction base="hvac:DuctRValue">
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R0.0"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R10"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R12"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R2.1"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R4.2"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R6"/>
                                                
                                                
                                                <xs:enumeration value="R8"/>
                                                
                                             
                                             </xs:restriction>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:simpleType>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F09_NotApplicableMessage" type="comp:NotApplicableMessage">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Installed New Return Duct R-Value</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled ==  NoNewDucts Or SupplyOnly 
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage
End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:choice>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:choice maxOccurs="1">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element maxOccurs="unbounded" name="F10_DuctMinimumRValueExceptions" type="comp:DuctMinimumRValueExceptions">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Exception from Min R-Value</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled == NoNewDucts 
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage
Else 
default result = NoException.  
End If
 
Allow user to override default and select one or both of the following: 
UninsulatedInDirectConditioning display term  Portions of ducts uninsulated  or less than R-6 in conditioned space
ALSO 
If F06_SupplyDuctLocation And F08_ReturnDuctLocation == ConditionedSpace 
allow user to select  RValueLT6EntirelyInConditioned display term  Ducts uninsulated or less than R-6 entirely in Conditioned Space
 
End if</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:appinfo source="displayterm">
                                                
                                                
                                                <ns2:displayterm value="UninsulatedInDirectConditioning">=Portions of duct system uninsulated or less than R-6 in conditioned space</ns2:displayterm>
                                                
                                             
                                             </xs:appinfo>
                                             
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F10_NotApplicableMessage" type="comp:NotApplicableMessage">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Exception from Min R-Value</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F04_NewDuctingInstalled == NoNewDucts 
result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage
End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:choice>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:element name="F11_CanRA3_3AirflowProtocolsTestSystem" type="comp:CanRA3_3AirflowProtocolsTestSystem">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:annotation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Can Approved Airflow Protocols be used to test this System?</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If C03_ResidentialHeatingSystemType Or C07_ResidentialCoolingSystemType  == DuctedMultiSplitHP, DuctedDuctlessMultiSplitHP, DuctedMultiSplitAC, DuctedDuctlessMultiSplitAC 
result = false display term No;
 
Else If C03_ResidentialHeatingSystemType Or C07_ResidentialCoolingSystemType  == CentralSplitAC, CentralSplitHP, CentralPackagedAC, CentralPackagedHP CentralLargePackagedAC, Or  CentralLargePackagedHP 
result = true display term Yes;  Else user selects from list: Yes (Boolean true value), No (Boolean false value).  End If 
Compliance check: If result == false then report in project status notes field that exemption from mandatory ECC verification of system airflow has been claimed.  Enforcement agency confirmation is recommended.</xs:documentation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:annotation>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:element>
                                    
                                    
                                    <xs:choice maxOccurs="1">
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F12_IndoorUnitNominalCoolingCapacity" type="hvac:IndoorUnitNominalCoolingCapacity">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Indoor Unit Nominal Cooling capacity (tons)</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If C12_IndoorUnitsCount GT 1 And C03_ResidentialHeatingSystemType Or C07_ResidentialCoolingSystemType   == VCHP_IndoorUnitDucted Or VCHP_IndoorUnitDuctedAndDuctless  
And one of the following is true: (F11_CanRA3_3AirflowProtocolsTestSystem == true And K03_RefrigerantChargeVerificationRequired == true) 
Or (Responses in B04, B05, B06, B07. B08 and B09 result in "DctLk" in the ECC column of the Logic Table for Determining Alteration type and ECC Verfication Requirements) 
Then user input numeric value x.xx; Else result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                       
                                       <xs:element name="F12_NotApplicableMessage" type="comp:NotApplicableMessage">
                                          
                                          
                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Indoor Unit Nominal Cooling capacity (tons)</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If C12_IndoorUnitsCount GT 1 And C03_ResidentialHeatingSystemType Or C07_ResidentialCoolingSystemType   == VCHP_IndoorUnitDucted Or VCHP_IndoorUnitDuctedAndDuctless  
And one of the following is true: (F11_CanRA3_3AirflowProtocolsTestSystem == true And K03_RefrigerantChargeVerificationRequired == true) 
Or (Responses in B04, B05, B06, B07. B08 and B09 result in "DctLk" in the ECC column of the Logic Table for Determining Alteration type and ECC Verfication Requirements) 
Then user input numeric value x.xx; Else result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicableMessage End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
                                          </xs:annotation>
                                          
                                       
                                       </xs:element>
                                       
                                    
                                    </xs:choice>
                                    
                                 
                                 </xs:sequence>
                                 
                              
