                                    <xs:documentation source="FieldText">If supplementary heating is gas, what is its rated input capacity (kBtu/hr)?</xs:documentation>
                                    
                                     
                                    <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If supplementary heating is not gas heating result = NotApplicable stored in NotApplicablemessage; </xs:documentation>
                                    
                                 
                                 </xs:annotation>
                                 
                              
