                                 <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Record Configuration of Controls.  Specify the mechanism for locking out supplementary heating</xs:documentation>
                                 
                                 
                                 <xs:documentation source="AdditionalRequirements">
                                    (for example, the name of the supplementary heating lockout setting in the thermostat setup, or the location and number of the specific dip switch, jumper, or dial that adjusts the lockout temperature)
If there is not mechanism to lockout supplementary heating above a temperature no greater than 35
                                    <ns1:deg/>
                                    F, this test fails.
                                 </xs:documentation>
                                 
                                 
                                 <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">User input text</xs:documentation>
                                 
                             
                              </xs:annotation>
                              
                          
